title: A Small Kiwi
description: Katie and Ashley help out a caller who has a dilemma with a possible jinx. Then, a slightly-longer-than-usual mental health update. Darius Leonard lost his wedding ring, and Katie has a theory why. Ashley sees Christian McCaffrey’s photoshoot for the first time. A pupdate AND a poopdate, and Katie calls Ashley and Travis old.
